            <title>[SOLR-7411] Thread safety issue in SearchHandler: unsafe publication of components</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7411</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Search handler falls prey to the double-checked locking bug for &quot;components&quot;:&lt;br/&gt;
